observe.desc:
      [
      {$0 vaguely resembles a humanoid with a cylindrical body and a face. It’s body seems to be made of a wooden core surrounded by soft sponge rubber sheathed in a tan cotton terry cloth. The face of the abnormality is drawn onto a grey cylinder with a neutal expression and exaggerated facial features.
}
      ]

      [
      {$0 is constantly generating heat around it and the process of how this heat is created is yet of unknown. The heat has been observed to have a positive effect on the mental health of agents. Especially agents with troubled childhoods or abusive parents seem to be comforted by the abnormality, this could be used to benefit the facility but further testing is required.
}
      ]

      [
      {<Oberservation Log #1_562>

	  <Redacted> grew up in the backstreets after losing his parents at a young age. He doesn’t interact with other staff often and enjoys working alone. For this test he was sent into Warm Mother’s containment to do attatchment work with her. Even though Warm Mother didn’t respond to any of <Redacted>’s interactions, after he left the containment he reported that he felt comforted during his visit.}
      ]

[
{<Oberservation Log #2_562>

<Redacted> was sent into Warm Mother's containment again. But this time he was in the containment for much longer. He started talking with Warm Mother and asked her questions like “Do you love me?” “Did my parents love me?”, when asked why he did this he said that it felt like the thing he should do and he also stated that he felt better about his past. His behaviour seems to have changed, to now be much more friendly and easygoing towards other staff.}
]

      [
      {<Oberservation Log #3_562>

	  <Redacted> was once again sent into Warm Mother's containment, he talked to Warm Mother and after cleaning the containment asked if she liked it, in the middle of the work he walked towards Warm Mother and hugged her. After there were no news from <Redacted> for 15 min, an agent went in to check on him. They found him passed out while hugging warm mother, during a subsequent medical exam on him the cause was determined to be malnutrition. To the question why he didn’t eat or drink for the last days he said: “The thought of leaving $0 terrified me.” He was ordered a psychological evaluation and testing with him is discontinued.}
      ]

      [
      {<Memo> 

	  <Redacted> did not show up for his evaluation a search team found his corpse hugging Warm Mother. He died due to dehydration. After this it was decided that no agent with a troubled background was allowed to work with Warm Mother for extended periods of time.}
      ]

      [
      {1 day later a piece of paper was found in Warm Mother's room

	  <Piece of paper>
"I am the perfect mother soft, warm, tender, a mother with infinite patience, a mother available twenty-four hours a day, a mother who never scolded her infant and a mother who loves all her children. But why then do all my children die? Why can I not keep those close to me alive? Why can I only give comfort and not life if I am supposed to be the perfect mother?".}
      ]
